           move      14                   to   w-scr-lun-ele          .
           perform   cmp-sng-fld-000      thru cmp-sng-fld-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * S-e-p-a-r-a-t-o-r-i                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "AA"                 to   w-scr-str-tip          .
