      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "fr"                 to   w-scr-str-tip          .
           move      w-scr-fso-cfr        to   w-scr-str-ele          .
           move      01                   to   w-scr-lun-ele          .
           perform   cmp-sng-fld-000      thru cmp-sng-fld-999        .
       exe-exp-mmz-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
