       exe-exp-zrm-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file area generica                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "mag "               to   f-xxx-are              .
           move      "zrm "               to   f-xxx-nam              .
           move      "std_mag_zrm"        to   f-xxx-npe              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
